        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 pl-1" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Wren Kitchens</strong> — widely popular in Nuneaton and Bedworth; Pindi fits Wren independently, without being tied to their retailer installation scheme. See the <a href="/retailers/wren/" style="color: var(--teal);">Wren installation page</a>.</span>
