            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Howdens Joinery</strong> — Pindi holds a trade account with Howdens, giving direct depot access and the ability to source components at trade price. See the <a href="/retailers/howdens/" style="color: var(--teal);">Howdens installation page</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Magnet</strong> — a popular mid-range choice across north Warwickshire; all Magnet ranges are fully compatible with independent installation.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>IKEA</strong> — IKEA's SEKTION and METOD kitchen systems are fitted regularly. Pindi is well-versed in IKEA's assembly and installation methodology.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Wickes and B&Q</strong> — both popular choices for Nuneaton homeowners fitting to a budget; the same precision and care is applied regardless of the kitchen's price point.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Benchmarx, DIY Kitchens, Kutchenhaus, Symphony, Masterclass</strong> — all covered as standard.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Premium and German brands</strong> — including Häcker, Nobilia, Mereway, Neptune, and deVOL, suited to larger properties in Weddington, Whitestone, and Attleborough.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          If your kitchen brand is not listed, call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> — in almost every case it can be accommodated.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <SupplierLogos />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Areas Within Nuneaton -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Areas of Nuneaton and Bedworth Covered
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi covers the whole of Nuneaton, Bedworth, and the surrounding north Warwickshire area across CV10, CV11, and CV12. He regularly works across:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Nuneaton Town &amp; Inner Areas</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Nuneaton town centre</strong> — Victorian terraces and post-war stock; compact kitchens benefiting from a careful survey-first approach</li>
              <li><strong>Stockingford</strong> — Established post-war residential; solid semis with modest kitchen footprints</li>
              <li><strong>Camp Hill</strong> — 1960s–80s housing with well-proportioned rooms and straightforward layouts</li>
              <li><strong>Galley Common</strong> — Settled residential area north-west of the town centre</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">East &amp; North Nuneaton</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Weddington</strong> — Larger detached and executive properties; premium installations suited to this area</li>
              <li><strong>Whitestone</strong> — Mixed residential close to the A444 corridor</li>
              <li><strong>Attleborough</strong> — Mature residential neighbourhood with varied property ages</li>
              <li><strong>Bermuda Park</strong> — Modern new-build estate; precise fitting required to manufacturer tolerances</li>
