            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Bedworth town centre</strong> — Victorian and inter-war terraces; chimney breast and alcove work common</li>
              <li><strong>Exhall</strong> — Post-war residential with straightforward access and solid construction</li>
              <li><strong>Bulkington</strong> — Village properties and newer residential on Bedworth's eastern edge</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Coverage &amp; Postcodes</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li>All CV10, CV11, and CV12 postcodes covered</li>
              <li>Surrounding north Warwickshire villages also covered</li>
              <li>Also covers nearby Coventry, Rugby, Leamington Spa, and Kenilworth</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Visit the <a href="/areas/nuneaton/" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">Nuneaton area page</a> for detailed postcode information, or call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> to confirm coverage for your address.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: What's Included & Pricing -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          What's Included in a Kitchen Fit — and How Pricing Works
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          A full kitchen fitting service from Pindi Sahota covers the complete installation from stripped room to finished kitchen. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 pl-1" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Stripping out the existing kitchen, disconnecting the sink and removing all appliances</span>
          </li>
